text: nnagadilinga lee tenetene gei e manawa lamalia mo nia daahili tenetene gi taga hailodo. Goodou ga hagalongo gi nia daangada ala e daahili i di nadau gaamai nadau wanga dehuia ang gi dogu Hale Daumaha. Digaula e daahili beenei,33.11 1 Kronikel 16.34; 2 Kronikel 5.13; 7.3; Ezra 3.11; Pisalem 100.5; 106.1; 107.1; 118.1; 136.1
